    "The plot indicates that topics in the range of 9-12 yields the highest coherence score around 0.4.",
    "In addition, topics around 90 show similar high coherence scores.",
    "This implies that when the topic is set between 9 and 12 or around 90, the model achieves an optimal solution.",
    "However, in this case, we chose 9 topics as our optimal number of LDA topics because the number appears more practicable.",
    "Moreover, we interrogate the topics in terms of human interpretability, and thus, when the topics are set to 9 the model produces distinct and interpretable topics/terms."
